Package: eolas
Title: Client for the eolas.fyi Statistical Data API
Version: 1.3.8
Authors@R: person("Virtus Solutions", email = "phil@virtus-solutions.io", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides convenient access to the eolas.fyi REST API
    (<https://api.eolas.fyi>), which serves 700+ official statistical and
    geospatial datasets from Stats NZ, the ABS, OECD, RBNZ, LINZ, NZTA, and
    more. Source-specific functions (eolas_get_statsnz(), eolas_get_oecd(),
    etc.) return tidy data frames ready for analysis with ggplot2, dplyr,
    or your favourite tooling.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/phildonovan/eolas-r, https://eolas.fyi
BugReports: https://github.com/phildonovan/eolas-r/issues
